Available September 15thSettle into this wonderful property full of mature trees and a park-like setting. 3 bed 1 and 1/2 half bath. Newer kitchen with stainless appliances, gorgeous hardwood floors, ceiling fans. Huge family room in lower level. Complete with 2 car garage, deck, and fenced yard. This house has it all including Forest Hills school district, and is move-in ready! Call us now to schedule your private showing!
<br><br><br>

If you are interested to text :-  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/cin/apa/7509019413/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>


